Paper: hep-th/0303142

Date: 2003-03-16

Title: One-dimensional Dirac oscillator in a thermal bath

Authors: M. H. Pacheco, R. R. Landim, and C. A. S. Almeida

Comments: 4 pages, 3 figures, to appear in Physics Letters A

We analyze the one-dimensional Dirac oscillator in a thermal bath. We foundthat the heat capacity is two times greater than the heat capacity of theone-dimensional harmonic oscillator for higher temperatures.